            <div class="preview-line short"></div>
            <div class="preview-line tall"></div>
            <span class="preview-page-label">Read it aloud. Does it sound like you?</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <span class="eyebrow">A Guide, Not a Cheat Sheet</span>
        <h2>You'll still write every word. That's the point.</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">
          We won't pretend this is a shortcut, because it isn't one — and we don't think you'd
          want it to be. Vows written for you tend to sound like it. This workbook exists to make
          the writing easier, not to do it for you.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted">
          You already have the feelings. The prompts inside are built to help you notice them,
          organize them, and put them into your own words — with enough structure that you never
          feel like you're starting from a blank page.
        </p>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/services/">Prefer more hands-on help? See our writing services {{ arrowRight("icon-arrow") }}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container-narrow text-center">
